Javadocs: IgnoCodeLib

Packages
net.paulhertz.aifile Package net.paulhertz.aifile provides dual functionality as a display list utility in Processing and as an export tool that writes to an Adobe Illustrator 7.0 file.
net.paulhertz.geom Package net.paulhertz.geom provides classes that handle geometric transforms.
net.paulhertz.util Package net.paulhertz.util currently provides classes that support permutations of integer arrays (such as lists of array indices) and various random number methods, including Gaussian distributions.
